    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>mushrooms have softened, add your <strong>pho broth paste</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min or until fragrant and most of the liquid has evaporated – these are your <strong>Vietnamese-style mushrooms</strong></p>",
