    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender, add a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and give everything a good mix up – these are your<strong> spicy potatoes</strong></p><p>Pop your<strong> hot dog bun[s] </strong>in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 30 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
