    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill the<strong> warmed hot dog bun[s] </strong>with the <strong>Vietnamese-style mushrooms </strong>and top with a little <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong>, <strong>sriracha </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> crispy fried onions</strong> – this is your<strong> Vietnamese-style mushroom</strong> <strong>bánh mì</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>spicy potatoes</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>quick-pickled slaw</strong> to the side, then with scissors, chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly over the <strong>bánh mì</strong> and <strong>potatoes</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
